{"tid":895531,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家既呀媽有冇成日都話要將屋企啲野俾人？","createTime":"2018-11-09T09:27:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-09T10:43:39.000Z","uid":174800,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"30ddfe41ea9379de60f0bcd64e7edb61ac6b72ca","tid":895531,"uid":174800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T09:27:09.000Z","msg":"我呀媽好搞笑 成日都話要拎屋企啲野俾人<br />\n我部ps4唔玩一排 又話要俾唔知邊個呀姨個仔<br />\n我妹啲名牌袋一排冇用 又話要送俾唔知邊個個女<br />\n上次我媽將我妹一袋未著過既衫 問都未問過佢就送俾人 之後嘈左穫金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩我媽宜家只夠膽郁我老豆啲野 上次問都冇問 將成疊餅卡送左俾人 前題係我老豆好鐘意食蛋糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家既呀媽係唔係都係咁？<br />\n<br />\n個個呀媽都一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得你呀媽咁撚奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔知大家呀媽最勁試過將屋企啲咩唔聲唔聲送俾人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bd2ecc8ebd34a0c7d0a66d4ff8b63760371dacb","tid":895531,"uid":2059,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T09:29:16.000Z","msg":"我媽反而係乜撚野都拎返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明屋企已經好多同類野.. <br />\n但一聽到話唔洗錢送俾佢，就有無需要都照攞<br />\n成屋都係野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59818cd945e6e9e7fd1ee8b25ce831a75a53a53f","tid":895531,"uid":4780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T09:30:30.000Z","msg":"留名睇連登仔廿四孝老母傑作<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75083e0518227f5ea19bc180a80a64d6bb331da5","tid":895531,"uid":1603,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1bd2ecc8ebd34a0c7d0a66d4ff8b63760371dacb","tid":895531,"uid":2059,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T09:29:16.000Z","msg":"我媽反而係乜撚野都拎